window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Battle for Terra Nova rages!</b></p> <p>The Triumvirate comes to conquer Terra Nova, landing an overwhelming assault by the surface by Netherguard and Ultari warships in orbit, laying siege to the human colony.</p> <p>As the battle grinds on, Governor Ken Hale leads the defenders in a desperate battle for survival. Hoping beyond hope that help will arrive in time to save them.</p> <p>Chief Kit Carson and her Pathfinders, with their new-found allies in tow, race home, praying they make it in time and that their efforts are enough to defeat Emperor Kyrios and his forces.</p> <p><i>Hale’s War</i> is the final installment in the Terra Nova Chronicles, taking readers on a wild ride or war, redemption, and salvation that culminates in this epic conclusion!</p>"; 
